---
// How It Works Section - Explains the four RootSpec skills
---

<section data-test="how-it-works-section" class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="how-it-works-container">
    <h2 class="how-it-works-title">How RootSpec Works</h2>

    <p class="how-it-works-intro">
      Transform any product idea into working, tested software through four simple skills.
    </p>

    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-card">
        <div class="skill-number">1</div>
        <h3 class="skill-title">/rs-init</h3>
        <p class="skill-description">
          Initialize your project structure and set up the RootSpec framework. Creates the foundation for specification-driven development.
        </p>
        <div class="skill-before-after">
          <span class="before">Before: Empty repository</span>
          <span class="after">After: Structured spec framework</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-card">
        <div class="skill-number">2</div>
        <h3 class="skill-title">/rs-spec</h3>
        <p class="skill-description">
          Build your complete specification through guided interviews. Transforms product descriptions into hierarchical, testable requirements.
        </p>
        <div class="skill-before-after">
          <span class="before">Before: Vague product ideas</span>
          <span class="after">After: Validated L1-L5 specification</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-card">
        <div class="skill-number">3</div>
        <h3 class="skill-title">/rs-impl</h3>
        <p class="skill-description">
          Implement features automatically from your validated specification. Generates working code with tests that match your acceptance criteria.
        </p>
        <div class="skill-before-after">
          <span class="before">Before: Specification ready</span>
          <span class="after">After: Working, tested features</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-card">
        <div class="skill-number">4</div>
        <h3 class="skill-title">/rs-validate</h3>
        <p class="skill-description">
          Continuously validate your implementation against specifications. Ensures your code stays aligned with your product philosophy.
        </p>
        <div class="skill-before-after">
          <span class="before">Before: Implementation complete</span>
          <span class="after">After: Validated, compliant software</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.how-it-works {
  padding: var(--space-64) 0;
  background: var(--color-surface-elevated);
}

.how-it-works-container {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--space-16);
}

.how-it-works-title {
  font-size: var(--text-3xl);
  font-weight: 700;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  color: var(--color-text);
}

.how-it-works-intro {
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-48);
  max-width: 600px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}

.skills-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-32);
}

.skill-card {
  background: var(--color-background);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: var(--space-24);
  position: relative;
  transition: transform 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease;
}

.skill-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

.skill-number {
  position: absolute;
  top: -12px;
  left: var(--space-24);
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: white;
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
}

.skill-title {
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  color: var(--color-primary);
  font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Monaco', 'Consolas', monospace;
  margin-top: var(--space-12);
}

.skill-description {
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
}

.skill-before-after {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--space-8);
}

.before,
.after {
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-12);
  border-radius: 6px;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.before {
  background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
  color: #dc2626;
}

.after {
  background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
  color: #16a34a;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .how-it-works {
    padding: var(--space-48) 0;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-24);
  }

  .skill-card:hover {
    transform: none;
  }
}

/* Reduce motion for accessibility */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .skill-card {
    transition: none !important;
  }

  .skill-card:hover {
    transform: none !important;
  }
}
</style>